{"title":"考古学者","authors":["陈樱"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":7,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"考古学者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈樱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏遍原始人的旧址"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在历史长河中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寻找"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉积了几百万年的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去而不返的刀耕火种"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你眼里复映出史诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逆人类生存之河而行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你拾取陶片审量祖先文明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你用石斧复制原始人的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你从火的灰烬中过滤人的智力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是艺术家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用手雕刻原始社会的艰辛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚下的路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连着一个个古老的支系"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在混沌迷茫之中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你发现清晰的人类意识在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现代社会的底座下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你挑选牢固的基石"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}